{{Politics of Libya under Muammar Gaddafi}}
The '''Declaration on the Establishment of the Authority of the People''' was brought into force on 2 March 1977 by the [[General People's Congress (Libya)|General People's Congress]], in the name of the [[Arab people]] of the [[Libyan Arab Jamahiriya]]. This [[amendment]] to the [[Constitution of Libya (1969)|constitution of 1969]] would remain in force until the adoption of the [[Libyan interim Constitutional Declaration|interim constitution]] on 3 August 2011.

